###PYRHNAS###
Ti Diakrinume sto Pyrhna?

-Diplh stoixeiwdhs membranh:
	-porous pou dhmiourgountai anamesa stis stibades twn diplwn membranwn
	kai enwnontai me fwsfolipidia gia na elegxoun ta makromoria pou 
	antalassontai metajy tous.

-Pyrhnoplasma:
	-Katalamvanei to megalytero meros tou pyrhna. Prokeite gia mia 
	hmirreusth ousia pou periexei sxedon to synolo tou DNA kai enan
	h perissoterous pyrnhniskous.
		-Pyrhniskoi:
			Diakrinetai eukola sto mikroskopio logw tou sfairikou sxhmatos
			kai ths pyknhs yfhs. Apoteleitai kyriws apo RNA & DNA, alla den
			perivalletai apo kapoia stoixeiwdh memvranh. Ston pyrhnisko 
			synti8etai to rRNA (systatiko riboswmatwn).	

Idiothtes Pyrhna:

-Fylassei to genetiko yliko (DNA). Me bash auto pou einai kategegrammeno ka8orizontai
oi idiothtes tou kyttarou kai kat' epektash tou organismou kai elegxontai oles oi kyttarikes
drasthriothtes.

-Einai to organidio sto opoio diplasiazetai to genetiko yliko, me tetoio tropo wste na 
ejasfalistei h metabibash twn genetikwn plhroforiwn, analloiwtwn, apo kyttaro se kyttaro
kai apo genia se genia.

-Einai to organidio sto opoio sto eswteriko tou synti8entai ta diafora eidh RNA (mRNA, rRNA,tRNA, snRNA). 

Yparxoun orismena kyttara opou kata thn diaforopoihsh tous exoun xasei ton pyrhna.
	-Ex. ta ery8ra aimsofairia.


###ENDOMEMBRANIKO SYSTHMA###
	Oi membranes tou kyttarou sygkrotoun ena eniaio domika & leitourgika synolo, to 
	endomembraniko systhma. Oi membranes tou, stoixeiwdhs kai mh, kallyptoum to 50% tou
	kyttaroy. Leitourgei ws enas koinos agwgos, pou epitrepei th metafora
	ousiwn anamesa sta diafora tmhmata tou kyttaroplasmatos kai pi8anotata anamesa tou
	pyrhna kai tou ejwkyttarikou peribalontos (diaforetika organidia). 

Apo ti apoteleitai?

-Endoplasmatiko Diktyo:

	-Adro Endoplasmatiko Diktyo:
		Auto to diktyo ferei sthn ejwterikh epifaneia twn membranwn tous mikrous
		sxhmatismous (riboswmata). Ta riboswmata den perivallontai apo kapoia
		membranh kai apotelountai apo rRNA & prwteines. Ekei ginetai kai h 
		prwteinosyn8esh. Meta th syn8esh oi prwteines eiserxontai sto eswteriko
		twn agwgwn. Ekei endexetai na ypostoun tropopoihseis (Ex. Pros8hkh Sakxarwn)
		Ta Riboswmata den yparxoun mono sthn epifaneia twn membranwn alla kai
		eleu8era sto kyttaroplasma ka8ws kai sta mitoxondria & xlwroplastes. Ta
		organidia auta exoun thn dynatothta na syn8etoun prwteines oi opoies einai
		aparaithtes, anejarthta apo to kyttaro. (Hmiautonoma Organidia)

	-Leio Endoplasmatiko Diktyo

-Symplegmata Golgi

-Lysoswmata

-Yperojeidioswmata

-Kenotopia
